免费注册”后登陆。</p><p>用微信小程序绑定的管理员微信扫描二维码，创建小程序。</p><p>4、点击“我管理的小程序”，进入小程序后台。</p><p>5、点击“营销应用”，选择合适的应用付费后点击营销应用列表进入相关设置。</p><p>6、点击装修设置选择相关配色，提交微信审核。</p><p>  （注：提交审核时所选服务类目一定要与营销应用上传的产品/服务一致）</p><p>7、小程序提交微信审核时间为3-7天，请耐心等待。</p><p>8、微信审核通过后，青否小程序后台点击立即发布，该小程序即发布成功。</p><p> </p><p>青否小程序6月15日前注册用户可免费使用青否小程序一年！</p><p>注册网站：<a href=\"http://www.qingful.com/\">www.qingful.com</a></p><p>客服 Q Q：<a href=\"http://wpa.qq.com/msgrd?v=3&uin=3367414088&site=qq&menu=yes\">3367414088</a></p><p><br></p>\r\n                                \r\n                                \r\n                                \r\n                                \r\n                                ","status":1,"type":0,"remark":"","rank":505,"created_at":"2017-06-09T07:19:59.000Z","updated_at":"2017-06-09T07:23:49.000Z","file":{"id":420,"name":"5953657959325138.jpg","ext":"jpg","type":"image/jpeg","savename":"89d97c40-4b2e-11e7-9ef3-a530d605fabf.jpg","savepath":"2017-06-07/","created_at":"2017-06-07T03:08:11.000Z","updated_at":"2017-06-07T03:08:11.000Z"}},{"id":143,"title":"【重磅出击】国内首家小程序平台即将上线！一键授权！30秒自动生成小程序！","pinyin":"chong-bang-chu-ji-guo-nei-shou-jia-xiao-cheng-xu-ping-tai-ji-jiang-shang-xian-yi-jian-shou-quan-30-miao-zi-dong-sheng-cheng-xiao-cheng-xu","file_id":370,"url":"","author":"kuaiduodian","sub":"国内首家小程序平台即将上线！\r\n全国招募99位内测伙伴，一年内免费使用！\r\n各种营销应用优先体验！","content":"                                    \r\n                                <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/aLZn32CBPk6lDiaKaPnHJ4jsh9nTu4aiaibcPicyQibJ2hagIEibQHqt6ge7D3dHtiaXW3KRDx1MsRMdcfJLGVbrtibTyA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=webp&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">国内首家小程序平台即将上线！</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">全国招募99位内测伙伴，一年内免费使用！</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">各种营销应用优先体验！</p><section><section><section><section><section><section><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><font color=\"#ff0000\"